
Operations:
    add, edit, delete, complete, complete all, reopen, reopen all, clear

Different operations:
    add large texts
    add as ctrl + V
    add few strings
    add without enter button
    edit as ctrl + V
    edit without enter button

Contexts-filters:
    - all
        add
        edit
        delete
        complete
        complete all
        clear
    - active
        add
        edit
        delete
        mark completed
        mark all completed
        clear
    - completed
        edit
        delete
        reopen
        reopen all
        clear

General:
    -items left
        add
        edit
        delete
        complete
        complete all
        clear

Switching between filters:
    -all
        available from active
        available from completed
    -active
        available from all
        available from completed
    -completed
        available from all
        available from active


